messages.content: How does the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension implement multiple workspaces?
It provides 5 quick workspace slots to work with flows.
What is the planned future of the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension?
The developer aims to automate the workspace selection and update process based on the flow.
What additional features would enhance the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension?
The developer suggests creating custom nodes to allow workspaces to be part of the workspace hierarchy.
Where can I find a video demonstrating the implementation of multiple workspaces in ComfyUI?
The developer has uploaded a video to YouTube showcasing the extension's functionality.
Where can I follow the developer's livestreams to learn more about the ComfyUI-MultiWorkspace extension?
The developer streams on Twitch at the channel Prozacgod.
